result.notes:
Spend by Rushmoor Borough Council over £500, as specified in the Transparency Code 2014

NB: From October 2014 Rushmoor are publishing spend above £250 as recommended in the Transparency code,
These datasets can be found here: http://data.gov.uk/dataset/rushmoor-250-spend

All transactions include non-recoverable VAT.

Where we made the payment to an individual or it is commercially sensitive, we have removed the names of suppliers and replaced them with either "Redacted personal data" or "Redacted commercially sensitive".

The Data currently follows our own schema - future releases will be migrated to the LGA recommended schema when possible.
